\f2\fs36 \cf4 John 6\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 Some time after this, Jesus crossed to the far shore of the Sea of Galilee (that is, the Sea of Tiberias),\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and a great crowd of people followed him because they saw the signs he had performed by healing the sick.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Just like many times in stories people are following Jesus because they want something from him\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then Jesus went up on a mountainside\'a0and sat down with his disciples.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The Jewish Passover Festival\'a0was near.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not sure what to do with this.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When Jesus looked up and saw a great crowd coming toward him, he said to Philip, \'93Where shall we buy bread for these people to eat?\'94\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe that this is the problem every Christian has \'96 or should have.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 6\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He asked this only to test him, for he already had in mind what he was going to do.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God knows how He is going to take care of your situation.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t have to worry about that\'85as a matter of fact, the only variable in this whole situation and the situation in your life is whether you are going to pass the test.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  The easy part is to think this is ultimately God\'92s job.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs32 \cf4 Matthew 14
\f3\b0\fs24   
\f2\b\fs18 \super 15\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub As evening approached, the disciples came to him and said, \'93This is a remote place, and it\'92s already getting late. Send the crowds away, so they can go to the villages and buy themselves some food.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 16\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jesus replied,\'a0\'93They do not need to go away. You give them something to eat.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is our responsibility\'85and it is easy to pass it off to someone else but it is ours.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Philip answered him, \'93It would take more than half a year\'92s wages to buy enough bread for each one to have a bite!\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And here is where so many of us get stuck\'85we completely understand what God is calling us to do\'85we can\'92t see HOW He\'92s going to do it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That is the tension in all of us\'85HOW for many of us trumps what every time.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I have a theory \'96 most of us know what we should be doing\'85we just don\'92t see HOW it can happen.  So we play dumb.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We would rather admit we are confused than we are a coward.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not the things we don\'92t know that hold us back in life\'85it\'92s the things we do know but refuse to do.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 8\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Another of his disciples, Andrew, Simon Peter\'92s brother,\'a0spoke up,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Here is a boy with five small barley loaves and two small fish, but how far will they go among so many?\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t have to understand to be available!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jesus said,\'a0\'93Have the people sit down.\'94\'a0There was plenty of grass in that place, and they sat down (about five thousand men were there).\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jesus then took the loaves, gave thanks,\'a0and distributed to those who were seated as much as they wanted. He did the same with the fish.\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 12\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When they had all had enough to eat, he said to his disciples,\'a0\'93Gather the pieces that are left over. Let nothing be wasted.\'94\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 13\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So they gathered them and filled twelve baskets with the pieces of the five barley loaves left over by those who had eaten.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
